located at /var/db/repos/gentoo/profiles/targets
Using nomultilib tarball one can still have the "profile" for plasma use flags by doing: 
cp /var/db/repos/gentoo/profiles/targets/desktop/plasma/package.use /etc/portage/package.use/plasma.use
equery uses opencv
will show you that it is actually applied.
rm the file to see the difference in output from equery.
